[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":215},["ShallowReactive",2],{"/2025/08/kde-customization":3,"surround-/2025/08/kde-customization":204},{"id":4,"title":5,"body":6,"categories":181,"date":183,"description":184,"draft":185,"extension":186,"image":24,"meta":187,"navigation":188,"path":189,"permalink":190,"readingTime":191,"recommend":196,"references":190,"seo":197,"sitemap":198,"stem":199,"tags":200,"type":190,"updated":190,"__hash__":203},"content/posts/2025/08/kde-customization.md","我的 KDE Plasma 6 美化方案分享",{"type":7,"value":8,"toc":168},"minimark",[9,13,17,20,25,29,32,36,39,48,51,54,61,64,67,70,152,155,158,165],[10,11,12],"h2",{"id":12},"前言",[14,15,16],"p",{},"最近个人把主力 Linux 系统从 CachyOS（Arch Linux）更换到了 Fedora 42（KDE Plasma Desktop Edition），对桌面也重新做了整理和美化，个人还是很喜欢 KDE Plasma 的，使用 Linux 也已有一年有余，今天分享下我目前使用的桌面美化方案。",[14,18,19],{},"一个好的美化方案不仅可以让自己赏心悦目，也可以通过组件位置合理放置提升个人的工作效率，个人不是很喜欢乱七八糟的动画效果或者过重美化，实际上整体方案还是很轻量的，使用到的插件和配色方案等均可在 KDE 商店下载到。",[21,22],"pic",{"caption":23,"src":24},"桌面效果图","https://blog-files.101045700.xyz/2025/08/kde-customization/kde-customization-priview01.webp",[21,26],{"caption":27,"src":28},"桌面带应用效果图","https://blog-files.101045700.xyz/2025/08/kde-customization/kde-customization-priview02.webp",[10,30,31],{"id":31},"方案",[33,34,35],"h3",{"id":35},"壁纸",[14,37,38],{},"桌面壁纸是使用的 Summer Pockets RB 内紬的其中一张 CG",[14,40,41,42],{},"图片地址（来自 Bilibili）：",[43,44,45],"a",{"href":45,"rel":46},"https://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/article/50acf57675d3e81a8af234cdeb9de307143d43b5.png",[47],"nofollow",[33,49,50],{"id":50},"上下布局",[14,52,53],{},"下方放置应用程序菜单栏，使用“图标任务管理器”实现类似 Dock 栏的效果，右部音乐播放器使用插件 PlasMusic Toolbar 实现。",[14,55,56,57],{},"音乐播放器插件 KDE 商店链接：",[43,58,59],{"href":59,"rel":60},"https://store.kde.org/p/2128143",[47],[14,62,63],{},"上方使用空面板，从左到右组件分别为“应用程序启动器”，“窗口列表”、“全局菜单”、“面板间隙”、“数字时钟”、“面板间隙”、“系统托盘”。",[33,65,66],{"id":66},"主题方案",[14,68,69],{},"前往 系统设置 ==> 全局主题 设置",[71,72,73,86],"table",{},[74,75,76],"thead",{},[77,78,79,83],"tr",{},[80,81,82],"th",{},"类型",[80,84,85],{},"名称",[87,88,89,98,106,114,121,128,136,144],"tbody",{},[77,90,91,95],{},[92,93,94],"td",{},"全局主题",[92,96,97],{},"Fedora",[77,99,100,103],{},[92,101,102],{},"颜色",[92,104,105],{},"Moe",[77,107,108,111],{},[92,109,110],{},"应用程序外观样式",[92,112,113],{},"Breeze 微风",[77,115,116,119],{},[92,117,118],{},"Plasma 外观样式",[92,120,105],{},[77,122,123,126],{},[92,124,125],{},"窗口装饰元素",[92,127,113],{},[77,129,130,133],{},[92,131,132],{},"图标",[92,134,135],{},"Colloid",[77,137,138,141],{},[92,139,140],{},"光标",[92,142,143],{},"Hoshino Swimsuit",[77,145,146,149],{},[92,147,148],{},"欢迎屏幕",[92,150,151],{},"Lagtrain",[33,153,154],{"id":154},"桌面时钟",[14,156,157],{},"使用 Redmi Clock 插件",[14,159,160,161],{},"KDE 商店链接：",[43,162,163],{"href":163,"rel":164},"https://store.kde.org/p/2175475",[47],[14,166,167],{},"如上，便是我目前全部的 KDE 美化方案了。",{"title":169,"searchDepth":170,"depth":170,"links":171},"",4,[172,174],{"id":12,"depth":173,"text":12},2,{"id":31,"depth":173,"text":31,"children":175},[176,178,179,180],{"id":35,"depth":177,"text":35},3,{"id":50,"depth":177,"text":50},{"id":66,"depth":177,"text":66},{"id":154,"depth":177,"text":154},[182],"技术探索","2025-08-28 05:30:00","文章分享了作者在 KDE Plasma 6 上的轻量级美化方案：选用 Fedora 42 系统，采用“图标任务管理器”做底部 Dock、顶部空面板配全局菜单的上下布局；主题以 Fedora 全局主题＋Moe 配色＋Breeze 样式为主，图标用 Colloid，光标用 Hoshino Swimsuit；桌面时钟和音乐播放分别使用 Redmi Clock 与 PlasMusic Toolbar 插件，所有资源均可在 KDE 商店下载。",false,"md",{},true,"/2025/08/kde-customization",null,{"text":192,"minutes":193,"time":194,"words":195},"3 min read",2.085,125100,417,10,{"title":5,"description":184},{"loc":189},"posts/2025/08/kde-customization",[201,202],"KDE","Linux","s5sxiBK-20TCr5IMU-yvxSXRvC7ZO-JMUXNEXdi84Bw",[205,210],{"title":206,"path":207,"stem":208,"date":209,"type":190,"children":-1},"《痴情哥哥与病弱妹妹的乡间生活》 Steam 版在 Linux/Deck 下的运行问题修复","/2025/06/sickly-days-linux-run","posts/2025/06/sickly-days-linux-run","2025-06-22 05:30:00",{"title":211,"path":212,"stem":213,"date":214,"type":190,"children":-1},"为 Clarity 主题增加 ResourceList 资源列表组件","/2025/10/clarity-resource-list","posts/2